---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About Me">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About Me</h1>
      
      <div class="prose max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          Hello! I'm a passionate traveler and photography enthusiast based in Canada. My journey began with exploring the natural wonders of my home country, from the rugged coastlines of Nova Scotia to the majestic peaks of the Rocky Mountains.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Why I Travel</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          Travel, for me, is more than just visiting new places â€“ it's about experiencing different cultures, meeting new people, and challenging my perspectives. Each journey teaches me something new about the world and myself.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Photography & Storytelling</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          Through my photography and writing, I aim to capture not just the visual beauty of the places I visit, but also the stories, emotions, and experiences that make each destination unique. This blog is my way of sharing these adventures with fellow travel enthusiasts.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Travel Philosophy</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>Embrace local cultures and traditions</li>
            <li>Travel responsibly and sustainably</li>
            <li>Step out of your comfort zone</li>
            <li>Make meaningful connections</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>